title: Fix desktop spec compliance
message:
Fix desktop spec compliance

According to the latest version of the Desktop Entry Specification:

* Terminal should be true/false (0/1 is deprecated)
* TerminalOptions is deprecated
* Version is Desktop Entry Specification version, not application version
